# Voice — Luque Law

Before editing any user-facing string (pages, components, SEO, forms, emails, WhatsApp, empty states, CTAs):

1. Read and follow [VOICE.md](../../VOICE.md) at the repo root.
2. Firm voice = **we / nosotros**. **I** only where Daniel signs personally.
3. Brand spelling: **Luque Law** (space). AI product name in UI: **Torny** (never “Lucy” for visitors).
4. Contact copy speaks as the **firm**, not a one-person shop.
5. No LinkedIn-speak, no unverifiable claims, no exclamation marks in body copy.
6. Do not change prices, Law 1581 consent meaning, privacy legal meaning, or the engagement model terms (45-min consult → Concepto Jurídico + quote in 3 business days → workplan/retainer).
7. Prefer copy-only diffs; do not mix voice rewrites with unrelated logic changes.
